text: Jeff McVean (born 21 December 1954) is an Australian equestrian. He competed at the 1984 Summer Olympics and the 1988 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1954 births Category:Living people Category:Australian male equestrians Category:Olympic equestrians of Australia Category:Equestrians at the 1984 Summer Olympics Category:Equestrians at the 1988 Summer Olympics Category:Place of birth missing (living people)
